00:00:49.350 --> 00:00:50.992
Once Upon A Time In Hollywood Plot Recap
________________

00:00:50.992 --> 00:00:54.770
Once Upon A Time is set to the backdrop of
the infamous Manson Murders, particularly

00:00:54.770 --> 00:00:56.250
the death of Sharon Tate.

00:00:56.250 --> 00:01:01.510
However, the film is somewhat satirical and
similar to Inglorious Basterds, the film gives

00:01:01.510 --> 00:01:04.110
the truth a rather more Hollywood ending.

00:01:04.110 --> 00:01:09.350
The movie itself follows Rick Dalton and his
friend Cliff Booth played by Leonardo DiCaprio

00:01:09.350 --> 00:01:11.330
and Brad Pitt respectively.

00:01:11.330 --> 00:01:14.530
Dalton was once at the top of his game, however,
all good things must come to an end and his

00:01:14.530 --> 00:01:17.560
career seems like it’s going on a complete
downward spiral.

00:01:17.560 --> 00:01:21.570
The film chronicles his journey to what he
thinks is the bottom rung of the ladder and

00:01:21.570 --> 00:01:26.189
along the way he and Booth bump into the likes
of many big real names in Hollywood including

00:01:26.189 --> 00:01:27.220
Bruce Lee.

00:01:27.220 --> 00:01:32.140
They also meet Catherine Share played by Lena
Dunham who just so happens to be the ringleader

00:01:32.140 --> 00:01:34.690
of the Manson girls which plays into the end.

00:01:34.690 --> 00:01:35.690
The Manson Crimes
________________

00:01:35.690 --> 00:01:40.330
On the whole, though the tale is mostly fictional
and after Dalton ends up getting married,

00:01:40.330 --> 00:01:44.740
he and Booth decide to part ways but they
want just one more night of drinking to celebrate

00:01:44.740 --> 00:01:46.480
all they’ve been through together.

00:01:46.480 --> 00:01:55.270
This just so happens to be on August the 8th,
which is my birthday by the way, and is, of

00:01:55.270 --> 00:01:59.590
course, the infamous night that four followers
of Charles Manson decided to murder Sharon

00:01:59.590 --> 00:02:02.079
Tate who just so happens to be a neighbour
of Dalton.

00:02:02.079 --> 00:02:06.080
In real life, they then went on to kill Tate
and her house guests.

00:02:06.080 --> 00:02:10.119
Manson did this to try and frame the Black
Panthers in order to start a race war that

00:02:10.119 --> 00:02:13.290
would eventually lead to the apocalypse known
as ‘Helter Skelter.’

00:02:13.290 --> 00:02:18.440
Though the murders did happen, Manson and
his followers were eventually jailed before

00:02:18.440 --> 00:02:22.579
the situation could escalate any more and
he and his followers went down in history

00:02:22.579 --> 00:02:25.280
as some of the worst serial killers of all
time.

00:02:25.280 --> 00:02:29.630
However, the film completely changes the events
from about this point onwards and paints out

00:02:29.630 --> 00:02:31.130
history with rose-tinted glasses.

